d":"5eacc314830a76c42dbbf2bf68d6a1c396a10e35","tid":2463354,"uid":112551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"蘇玉華勁有氣質<br />\n個林琳成隻北姑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f731791de9304c05b91e92002fd38794d6d563fc","tid":2463354,"uid":1441,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fb5f6c9ddbc86e2ccf04497bb937d6f8e0aaafa3","tid":2463354,"uid":244612,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"f23b7444213ee9edca2f47122320a28fa67331f8","tid":2463354,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:33:17.000Z","msg":"不過，有港台中人說，雖然蘇玉華表示只答應拍兩集，但其實是被換走的。消息指，助理廣播處長（電視及機構業務）區麗雅曾向電視部員工表明：「以後都唔可以搵蘇玉華」，因蘇「好明顯畀人睇到係咩顏色」，相信周五晚的《鏗鏘說》很可能是蘇最後一次在擔任港台電視節目主持。<strong>消息續指，昨（24日）傳出相關報道後，管理層今日表現大為緊張，亦有多個會議。</strong><br />\n.....<br />\n至於被傳將接替《鏗鏘說》主持一職的<strong>林琳</strong>，她今接受《蘋果》訪問時表示，自己從未收到製作組邀請，不清楚為何會有相關消息傳出。她指，若然受到邀請，會考慮接受，稱自己最近有不少主持節目的經驗，包括在港台擔任英文電台節目主持。她稱願意嘗試不同機會，但不肯定《鏗鏘說》對主持的要求，相信需要做更多準備工作。<br />\n<br />\n林稱，不認為自己是因為民建聯成員身份才被傳接替主持，只是這個身份容易成為討論焦點，「<strong>民建聯係原罪嚟㗎嘛，如果搵第二個又會話另一樣啦</strong>」。她指，港台其實有不同節目，「黃藍」兩邊人物都會邀請，例如自己都曾經接受《鏗鏘集》訪問，認為節目最重要是「balance（平衡）、左右都有」，而暫時認為港台節目都有符合相關要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210325/EPUKWN32HVFETJWLDWKRNGL65M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210325%2FEPUKWN32HVFETJWLDWKRNGL65M%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=0be71a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210325%2FEPUKWN32HVFETJWLDWKRNGL65M%2F&h=90f970a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210325/EPUKWN32HVFETJWLDWKRNGL65M/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"其實係因為so辱華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"咁應該搵談辱英做主持啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76169e84fcfea287b5bb68f30b9a7497a56c880f","tid":2463354,"uid":268076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"港台高層歧視有色人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95559a8982300ebe9a5b82a49b286f687938855f","tid":2463354,"uid":392280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f954b8c740429775d26a952358906db42b64006d","tid":2463354,"uid":156652,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://storage.cloudconvert.com/tasks/7cf9752e-bbd7-43bb-b97d-27128b981d37/LIHKG--fbdown.net.gif?AWSAccessKeyId=cloudconvert-production&amp;Expires=1616859201&amp;Signature=mqNZlTRh1gVe65GRYXlXnO5khsE%3D&amp;response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22LIHKG--fbdown.net.gif%22&amp;response-content-type=image%2Fgif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.cloudconvert.com%2Ftasks%2F7cf9752e-bbd7-43bb-b97d-27128b981d37%2FLIHKG--fbdown.net.gif%3FAWSAccessKeyId%3Dcloudconvert-production%26Expires%3D1616859201%26Signature%3DmqNZlTRh1gVe65GRYXlXnO5khsE%253D%26response-content-disposition%3Dattachment%253B%2520filename%253D%2522LIHKG--fbdown.net.gif%2522%26response-content-type%3Dimage%252Fgif&h=8b8d9879&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83e65513156a0e6a0cb12716f0eee2e415f4277","tid":2463354,"uid":6024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"蘇玉華去杜生個台啦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b3f5486b6816d62c6dba0d30c524bf9444ef90","tid":2463354,"uid